views.markdown: If you need help with "DankTime", you can contact Mark Kuebel, the developer, via e-mail.
Mark Kuebel is the maintainer of the package "DankTime". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "pandather's repo" repo, Mark J. Kuebel.
